---
---

<section class="verticals" id="verticals">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="v-header reveal">
      <span class="v-kicker">Cómo trabajamos juntos</span>
      <h2 class="v-title">Tres formas de generar <em>demanda B2B</em>.</h2>
      <p class="v-desc">Elegí cómo querés avanzar: que lo hagamos nosotros, que te enseñemos a hacerlo, o que construyamos el activo digital que convierte.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="v-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 — Asesoría -->
      <a href="/web/asesoria" class="v-card reveal">
        <div class="v-card-top">
          <div class="v-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="v-label">Te enseñamos</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="v-card-title">Asesoría 1:1 en generación de demanda.</h3>
        <p class="v-card-desc">Clases individuales en las que te entregamos nuestro sistema completo de prospección B2B. Salís con scripts, listas, secuencias y métricas funcionando.</p>
        <ul class="v-bullets">
          <li>Sesiones individuales según tu nivel</li>
          <li>Plantillas, scripts y SOPs</li>
          <li>Aplicado a tu propio negocio</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="v-cta">Ver asesoría
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="14" height="14"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 2 — Outbound (FEATURED) -->
      <a href="/web/outbound-gestionado" class="v-card v-card-featured reveal">
        <span class="v-badge">Más elegido</span>
        <div class="v-card-top">
          <div class="v-icon v-icon-featured" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="v-label v-label-featured">Lo hacemos por vos</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="v-card-title">Outbound completo gestionado.</h3>
        <p class="v-card-desc">Llenamos tu agenda con clientes calificados sin que muevas un dedo. Diseñamos, ejecutamos y optimizamos un sistema multicanal end-to-end.</p>
        <ul class="v-bullets">
          <li>LinkedIn Sales Navigator + Email + Meta + Google</li>
          <li>+500 reuniones agendadas en 24 meses</li>
          <li>Reportes semanales y dashboard en vivo</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="v-cta v-cta-featured">Ver outbound completo
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="14" height="14"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 3 — Web Dev -->
      <a href="/web/desarrollo-web" class="v-card reveal">
        <div class="v-card-top">
          <div class="v-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/><path d="m7 9 2 2-2 2M11 13h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="v-label">Construimos tu web</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="v-card-title">Landing pages y sites que convierten.</h3>
        <p class="v-card-desc">Diseñamos y desarrollamos tu activo digital pensado para captar reuniones, no solo para verse bien. Performance, SEO y copy en un solo paquete.</p>
        <ul class="v-bullets">
          <li>Diseño + desarrollo + copywriting</li>
          <li>Optimizado para conversión y SEO</li>
          <li>Lighthouse 95+ en todos los ejes</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="v-cta">Ver desarrollo web
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="14" height="14"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.verticals {
  padding: 6rem 0 5rem;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}
.v-header {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
}
.v-kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--accent);
  background: var(--accent-light, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08));
  padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.v-title {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.v-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
.v-desc {
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 520px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.v-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.15fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  align-items: stretch;
}

.v-card {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: var(--card, #fff);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08));
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 2rem 1.75rem 1.75rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--text);
  transition: all 0.35s var(--ease);
  overflow: hidden;
  isolation: isolate;
}
.v-card::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0) 0%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.03) 100%);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.35s var(--ease);
  z-index: -1;
}
.v-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  border-color: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
}
.v-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

.v-card-featured {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1625 0%, #2a1f3d 100%);
  border-color: transparent;
  color: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.15);
  transform: translateY(-8px);
}
.v-card-featured:hover {
  transform: translateY(-12px);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.25);
}
.v-card-featured::before {
  background: radial-gradient(600px 300px at 50% 0%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18), transparent 60%);
  opacity: 1;
}

.v-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.25rem;
  right: 1.25rem;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  color: #fff;
  background: var(--accent);
  padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.35);
}
.v-badge::before {
  content: "";
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #fff;
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

.v-card-top {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.v-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.06);
  color: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 12px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.v-icon-featured {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
  color: #c4b5fd;
}
.v-label {
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  color: var(--text2);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.v-label-featured { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); }

.v-card-title {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  line-height: 1.25;
  letter-spacing: -0.4px;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: inherit;
}
.v-card-featured .v-card-title { color: #fff; }

.v-card-desc {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--text2);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.v-card-featured .v-card-desc { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); }

.v-bullets {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.55rem;
  flex: 1;
}
.v-bullets li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--text2);
}
.v-bullets li::before {
  content: "";
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.10);
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236d28d9' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='20 6 9 17 4 12'/></svg>");
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.v-card-featured .v-bullets li { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }
.v-card-featured .v-bullets li::before {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.22);
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%23c4b5fd' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='20 6 9 17 4 12'/></svg>");
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
}

.v-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-top: auto;
  align-self: flex-start;
  padding: 0.55rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.25s var(--ease);
}
.v-cta svg { transition: transform 0.25s var(--ease); }
.v-card:hover .v-cta svg { transform: translateX(3px); }
.v-cta-featured {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 0.65rem 1.15rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  align-self: stretch;
  justify-content: center;
}
.v-card-featured:hover .v-cta-featured { background: #7c3aed; }

@media (max-width: 960px) {
  .v-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .v-card-featured { transform: none; order: -1; }
  .v-card-featured:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .verticals { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  .v-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
}
</style>
